Package it.unicam.cs.pa.jbudget105053.model

Interface Movement

  • All Superinterfaces:
    HasID
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BasicMovement
    public interface Movement
extends HasID
    This interface extends the interface HasID and is implemented by all the classes that have the responsibility to manage a single movement. It allows to get the information related to the movement: ID, type of movement, money amount, date, associated account, associated transaction and the list of all the tags associated with the movement. Each movement derives its date from the transaction it is associated with.
